### Description

`undefined` is missing from the returned type of "selected" in MatSelect. It can return undefined if the selected list is empty: `this._selectionModel?.selected[0]`
at https://github.com/angular/components/blob/46cfbe566ab99207c3951c6c86aed20f65d925a6/src/material/select/select.ts#L668-L670

